data.name: OtherPlaceId.ToolTip
data.value: Ignore this textbox unless you know what you are doing. This textbox allows you to see servers from a different place id than the one you have in the main window. This can be used for games such as deepwoken, you can put in the depths or etrean luminant PlaceId and have it show servers for them. While having an ID in the textbox, you can right click on a server, click "Join", and once a beep plays, roblox matchmaking will put you into that server.
